	<p>About the lab.</p>-->
	<div class="row" style="margin-top:5%;">
		<div class="col-lg-7">
			<h5>We are the Georgia Tech Visual Analytics Lab.</h5>
			The goal of our research is to develop interactive visual analytic applications that <b>help people make sense of data.</b> We approach this challenge through combining scientific techniques from information visualization, machine learning, data mining, and human-computer interaction to produce usable, yet powerful visual analytic applications.
		</div>
		<div class="col-lg-5">
