				<li><a href="http://bahadorsaket.com/" target="_blank">Bahador Saket</a> gave an invited talk titled <i>Visualization by Demonstration</i> at the <a href="https://sites.google.com/math.arizona.edu/tripodssummerconference2019/home">2019 TRIPODS Southwest Conference </a></li>
